clone this repo - then all you need to do is install nodejs (with npm) 
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs 
sudo apt-get install -y build-essential
>npm init 
to set up the node modules required
>gulp 
to run the transpile, bundle and watch 
>npm start 
to run the http-server on port 80

Boom

